<HEADLINE> Chinese Acrobats Add Fun to 111st Birthday of </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MAPUTO, November 10 (Xinhua) -- Chinese acrobats Tuesday added
much fun to the festivity of the 111st birthday of Maputo, the
capital city of Mozambique.
</P>
<P>
Eighteen young artists from the Chinese Acrobatic Troupe gave
their first performance at the Red Star Stadium in Maputo Tuesday
morning to the warm welcome of 500 enthusiastic Mozambicans.
</P>
