head, without dropping even one. This item won a gold medal in
the world acrobatics competition in Hungary earlier this year.
</P>
<P>
One Mozambican lady said she really enjoyed the show, saying
"it is really beautiful."
</P>
<P>
The Chinese troupe is scheduled to offer five shows in Maputo
before leaving for other African countries including South
Africa. 
