percent.
</P>
<P>
It was another dismal day for Royal Bank of Scotland. The
shares tumbled another 4 percent.
</P>
<P>
In Frankfurt Xetra DAX slid 81 points, 1.7 percent, to close at
4,681.34.
</P>
<P>
In Paris the CAC 40 eased 1.1 percent, to 3,544.74.
</P>
<P>
In Zurich SMI dropped 87 points, 1.3 percent, to 6,654.1.
