cultural activities such as exhibitions and theatrical
performances.
</P>
<P>
The agreement was signed by Vassos Pirgos, permanent secretary
of the Cypriot Ministry of Communications and Works, and Bernard
Fournier, senior official of the French Ministry of Public Works,
Housing, Transport and Tourism. 
