<TEXT>
<P>
BEIRUT, November 10 (Xinhua) -- The U.S. Commerce Secretary
William Daley is to visit Lebanon Thursday to boost bilateral trade
ties, the independent Central News Agency reported Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
