economic officials and businessmen in private sector to study the
possibility for the U.S. investment in Lebanon, the agency said.
</P>
<P>
Lebanon is part of Daley's Mideast tour, which also includes
stops in Israel, Egypt, Jordan and the Palestinian self-ruled
areas. 
