<TEXT>
<P>
MANILA, November 11 (Xinhua) -- The Presidential Palace of the
Philippines said the proposed budget for 1999 contains no pork
barrel fund, a government appropriation for local improvements
designed to ingratiate legislators with their constituents, the
Philippines News Agency said Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
The agency quoted the presidential spokesman Jerry Barican as
