<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, November 11 (Xinhua) -- The gold price in Hong Kong
rose 16 HK dollars to close at 2,706 HK dollars a tael Wednesday,
according to Po Sang Bank, one of the major gold dealers in Hong
Kong.
</P>
