<HEADLINE> New Zealand Stocks Close Lower </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WELLINGTON, November 11 (Xinhua) -- The New Zealand share
market closed lower here Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
The NZSE40 Index ended 20 points lower at 1,987 with a turnover
 of 79 million NZ dollars (41.9 million U.S. dollars).
</P>
