<HEADLINE> October Interbank Turnover 3.952 Billion Yuan </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, November 11 (Xinhua) -- Transactions on Shanghai's
interbank market were 3.952 billion yuan in October.
</P>
<P>
That translates into a daily turnover of 189 million yuan for
the 20 trading sessions.
</P>
<P>
The interest rate on the interbank money market averaged 5.18
percent in October, up 0.11 percentage point from the end of
September.
</P>
<P>
Statistics show spot bond trading of 87.4 million yuan in
October and trading in bond repurchasing of 11.099 billion
yuan. The average interest rate on bond repurchasing was 4.85
percent, down 0.14 percentage point from September. 
