<HEADLINE> Myanmar, Singapore Specialists Jointly Perform </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
YANGON, November 11 (Xinhua) -- Surgical operations were
jointly performed here on Tuesday by Myanmar and Singapore
specialists.
</P>
<P>
The orthopedic operations on patients were carried out at the
Defense Services Orthopedic Hospital by visiting Singapore
orthopedists, led by Dr. Yeo Seng Jin, and their Myanmar
counterparts, led by Colonel Than Myint, Commandant of the
hospital, official The New light of Myanmar reported Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
